        Install
        =======
        
        .. code-block:: sh
        
            pip3 install ninjecto
        
        
        Changelog
        =========
        
        0.2.0 (2020-02-03)
        ------------------
        
        Fix
        ~~~
        
        - Rendered files will now have the same permissions as the source files.
        
        
        0.1.1 (2020-02-03)
        ------------------
        
        Fix
        ~~~
        
        - Fixes TypeError caused by invalid value of the levels parameter.
        
        
        0.1.0 (2020-02-01)
        ------------------
        
        New
        ~~~
        
        - Development preview.
        
        
